q: SELECT a/${path} FROM EHR e[ehr_id/value='${ehr_id}'] CONTAINS COMPOSITION c[openEHR-EHR-COMPOSITION.test_all_types.v1] CONTAINS SECTION s[openEHR-EHR-SECTION.test_all_types.v1] CONTAINS ACTION a[openEHR-EHR-ACTION.test_all_types.v1] WHERE (c/uid/value = '${c_uid}' AND a/description[at0001]/items[openEHR-EHR-CLUSTER.test_all_types.v1]/items[at0001]/items[at0002]/items[at0003]/value/value = true)
